name: Deconstructed Donut on Acid .png
description:
Philipp Merkelbach (twitter: @flipsflop3000) vs Eliot theSuper (twitter: @ELIOTbk) collabo for DONUTS4HEN . 2021 . 
Based on a lowpoly Model by Eliot, Philipp created this awesome render in his personal style and inspiration .
This is also part of a VR-Gallery around the creation of a "Giant Donut" analog sculpture by Eliot .
Celebrating analog/digital artistic expression and the new medium of NFT and digital consumtion for the large-scale exhibition in "Kunstlabor 2", organized by "MUCA" Museum of Urban and Contemporary Art in Munich .
There is also a "Donut GLB" file to this work as an own mint - completing this mini Acid-Donut collection!
